OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,F's Environment & Infrastructure
OL,7,FCommittee has published a new strategy
OL,8,Fsetting out the improvements they want
OL,9,Fto make to the island's road network.
OL,11,FThe Better Transport Plan also aims to
OL,12,Fprovide a basis on how best to connect
OL,13,Fexisting and new roads with several up
OL,14,Fand coming housing developments - the
OL,15,Fmajority of which are in the north of
OL,16,Fthe island.
