OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,FAll together, more than 1000 new homes
OL,7,Fare expected to be built across sites
OL,8,Fsuch as; the Fontaine Vinery, Les Bas
OL,9,FCourtils, Pointes Rocques, Franc Fief,
OL,10,FSaltpans Key Industrial Estate Area,
OL,11,FCleveleys Vinery, Saltpans and Leale's
OL,12,FYard.
OL,14,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez, President
OL,15,Fof E&I said: "Our road infrastructure
OL,16,Fis already not serving residents in
OL,17,Fthe north anywhere near as well as it
OL,18,Fcould.
