OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,F"This Plan will guide improvements to
OL,7,Ftransport options as those
OL,8,Fdevelopments move forward. We want to
OL,9,Fbe proactive in our efforts to
OL,10,Fminimise any negative impacts of
OL,11,Flikely new development and use the
OL,12,Fopportunity to create in the process
OL,13,Fsome additional benefits for the
OL,14,Fcurrent and future residents alike."
OL,16,FThe committee says that having this
OL,17,Fplan in place will "pave the way for a
OL,18,Fwider and better range of transport
OL,19,Fchoices" with the hope that more
OL,20,Fislanders will choose to use buses,
OL,21,Fbikes and travel by foot.
