OL,3,CGuernsey States unveil strategy to
OL,4,Cimprove island's transport network
OL,6,FOther suggestions to ease transport
OL,7,Finclude: new footpaths, new bike
OL,8,Fpaths, extending a one-way system with
OL,9,Fa cycling contraflow, improved bus
OL,10,Froutes and schedules, better
OL,11,Fjunctions, improved signage and a new
OL,12,Ftravel app.
OL,14,FHowever, the committee warns that any
OL,15,Fwork completed under the plan will be
OL,16,Fintroduced in stages and state that
OL,17,Fany changes will be "practical,
OL,18,Fdeliverable and affordable".
